// 2. The Python Backend Server
`1 /
/: Python | server.py \
from fastapi import FastAPI
import uvicorn

app = FastAPI()

@app.get("/")
def read_root():
    return {"status": "OMNI Engine Mega-App is Online and fully functional!"}

if __name__ == "__main__":
    uvicorn.run(app, host="127.0.0.1", port=8000)
/
\ 1`

